   3. How often do you visit ED's web site? (Please check only one)

   (*) Daily
   ( ) At least once a week
   ( ) At least once a month
   ( ) At least once every six months
   ( ) Less than once every six months

   4. Have you registered with My.ED.gov, ED's web personalization
   feature? (Please check only one)

   (*) Yes
   ( ) No (Please skip to Question #10)

   5. If you have registered with My.ED.gov, ED's web personalization
   feature, what are the main reasons? (Please check all that apply)

   [ ] I like personalization in general.
   [ ] I want to focus on what ED has for me specifically and filter out
   the rest.
   [ ] I want to find news in my areas of interest.
   [ ] I want to be able to find my favorite pages quickly.
   [ ] I want to see all the information on my favorite topics in one
   place.
   [ ] I was curious.
   [ ] No particular reason.
   [ ] Other (please specify) ______________________________

